{"tid":670783,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"老母唔比我參加遊學團 同佢吵左大獲","createTime":"2018-05-19T16:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T07:22:31.000Z","uid":5995,"like":39,"dislike":571,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"472a1ed2bb8202b1ced51756a4ce522dce7aa045","tid":670783,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:05:33.000Z","msg":"我16歲 過埋暑假就升中四<br />\n學校搞左個遊學團暑假去澳洲14日<br />\n團費9000$ 學校資助左一半<br />\n滿心歡喜同老母講想參加<br />\n佢一句撻埋黎話唔得<br />\n我問點解<br />\n佢話屋企冇錢 得老豆一個做野<br />\n要交租 電費水費好貴 個個月都冇淨<br />\n叫我生性 暑假去小童群益會到學下野就算啦 <br />\n幾百蚊都仲負擔到<br />\n我唔服氣<br />\n點解張文傑(我同學)屋企人又比錢佢去呀 佢又係住呢條村 <br />\n我老母即刻冇聲出 <br />\n我嬲到離街出走左<br />\n依家係樓下公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我未出過國 飛機都未搭過 真係好想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c74a32cd57a0040cc13a0d9ae1754ede106ecba","tid":670783,"uid":24472,"like":168,"dislike":4,"score":164,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:08:40.000Z","msg":"你咪去幫你個同學打下飛機，賺下啲錢囉"},{"pid":"0aa8fd07eef5327d53e5490f96e5557f7e01fef9","tid":670783,"uid":5995,"like":195,"dislike":11,"score":184,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/001035_87c13aa63f466d8c3a81713eee89e6f1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F001035_87c13aa63f466d8c3a81713eee89e6f1.png&h=665cf704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屋企仲開住燈 <br />\n唔想返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b4346c66d7b571de49ccb06c4a1003aa00bb68","tid":670783,"uid":136186,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:12:42.000Z","msg":"男定女 女嘅去做ptgf"},{"pid":"1d88f3e30912da8c72d0dafa4cdc68ef372681c9","tid":670783,"uid":174321,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:13:37.000Z","msg":"樓主讀羅中？你屋企咁似麗x嘅<img src=\"/as